name: We Are All Where We Belong
description:
This item is a digital download of Quiet Company's new album, We Are All Where We Belong, which was released October 4th.

You will receive your download code via email within 24 hours of your order.

Please note that this item no longer comes with 3 months of Grooveshark Anywhere.

For CD or Vinyl versions of this album, please visit http://www.quietcompanymusic.com/shop

A personal note from Quiet Company:

"Thank you so much for ordering our new album 'We Are All Where We Belong.' We hope you’ll enjoy it as much as we enjoy ninjas, robots, ninja turtles, robotic ninjas & especially robotic turtles. We hope you’ll come befriend us on Facebook & Twitter so you can tell us what you think about the album & we can tell you when we’ll be in your town."

Tracklist:

1. The Confessor (You Could Exist Without It)
2. You, Me, & The Boatman (Truth Is, I've Been Thirsty My Whole Life)
3. Preaching To The Choir Invisible, Part I (What Do You Think Happens When We Die?)
4. Set Your Monster Free (My New Year's Resolution Is To Cope With My Morality)
5. We Went To The Renaissance Fair (...All Our Friends Were There)
6. Fear & Fallacy Sitting In A Tree (You Were Doing Well Until Everyone Died)
7. Are You A Mirror? (Or A Window?)
8. Everything Louder Than Everything Else (Xanadu Clambake, Point Zion, Ri, Summer 2001)
9. The Black Sheep & The Shepherd (Look, I'm Just An Instrument, Okay?)
10. The Easy Confidence (What I Would Say To You Now)
11. Midnight at The Lazarus Pit (The Harlot and The Beast Are Dating!)
12. Preaching to the Choir Invisible, Part II (What Do You Think Happens When We Live?)
13. Never Tell Me The Odds (This Is The Worst Crazy Sect I've Ever Been In)
14. At Last! The Celestial Being Speaks (The Utterly Indifferent)

name: Grooveshark Headphones + 3 Months of Anywhere
description:
Premium sound, premium materials, and premium style enable these customized headphones from Frends to pack a heavy punch. If you need a headphone that can make all your dreams come, true look no further. These headphones deliver a custom tuned driver with inter changeable caps, complete modular construction, and minimal design to ensure you experience all your music has to offer.

Grooveshark x Frends headphones come with 3 free months of Grooveshark Anywhere (a $27 value), and for a limited time, a free pair of Grooveshark shades! 


From Frends:
 
We believe that our products should be the perfect blend of form and function. Our headphones have the deliberate design lines and fashion cues that our crew of athletes, musicians and artist expect. This blend of forms is held in balance by providing the function that their active lifestyles demand.

For a first-hand look into the Frends way of life, check out 
http://www.wearefrends.com/story.html and http://www.wearefrends.com/frends-vision.html


--
Tech Specs:

1KHZ Sensitivity/103dB
Custom tuned 40mm driver
Custom designed mic, strain relief & audio jack
Low-profile and light
Multi-function mic 
Asymmetrical body
90-degree plug
Cable manager
32-ohm impedance
Memory-foam ear cushion
Tangle-free durable TPE cord
Compatible with iPod, iPad, iPhone
20-20,000Hz frequency range
Free mic
